      <h3>Is Jobsolv really free?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Jobsolv offers a forever-free plan that includes access to the job board, resume builder, job tracker, and limited resume tailoring. Jobhire.ai requires payment to use.</p>

      <h3>Does Jobhire.ai tailor resumes for each job?</h3>
      <p>No. Jobhire.ai uses AI resume rewriting but doesn't tailor resumes for each specific job posting. Jobsolv customizes your resume for every application, matching keywords and skills from each job description.</p>

      <h3>Which tool gets more interviews?</h3>
      <p>Jobsolv typically generates higher interview rates because each application is tailored to the specific job. Jobhire.ai focuses on volume, which may reduce relevance for specific roles.</p>

